question_text: What do you mean by data science?
option_a: Dealing with huge amounts of data to find marketing patterns is known as data science
option_b: Extracting a meaningful insight from the data is what data science is
option_c: It is a study that deals with a huge amount of all types of data structured, unstructured, or semi-structured D)All of the above Answer:

option_a: Structured data is a type of data that is huge in number and has many inaccurate values
option_b: Structured data is a type of data that is very less in number and can be stored in proper rows and columns
option_c: Structured data is a type of data that has inaccurate values but can be stored in rows and columns
